---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Case Study: HoloLux Torino - Showroom immersivi e NFC | Bitora"
  description="Anteprima del progetto HoloLux Torino: ecosistema digitale con showroom immersivi, tessere NFC e automazioni lead." 
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 via-white to-primary/20 dark:from-indigo-950/40 dark:via-black dark:to-primary/20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Case Study in aggiornamento</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">HoloLux Torino</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Percorso consulenziale per unire showroom immersivi, tessere NFC e flussi di lead automation dedicati al settore esperienziale.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-lg dark:bg-black/50">
            <div class="grid gap-4 text-sm text-left text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 md:grid-cols-3">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Settore</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Tecnologia immersiva B2B</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Durata setup</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">4 settimane</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Stato</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-semibold text-primary">In fase di rifinitura contenuti</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr,0.9fr] lg:items-start">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Panoramica rapida</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Obiettivo: trasformare la presenza digitale di HoloLux in un percorso coerente tra online e showroom fisico, facilitando richieste demo e follow-up automatici.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Audit sul posizionamento attuale e analisi dei flussi commerciali.</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Blueprint operativo con sito modulare, gallerie immersive e narrazione di progetto.</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Implementazione tessere NFC e landing dedicate per il booking demo.</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Automazioni CRM e analytics per tracciare ogni visita e interazione.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <aside class="glass-panel rounded-3xl p-6 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Metriche preliminari</h3>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-primary">+45%</strong> richieste demo nelle prime 8 settimane</li>
              <li><strong class="text-primary">3×</strong> velocità di follow-up commerciale</li>
              <li><strong class="text-primary">24/7</strong> prenotazioni demo tramite landing dedicate</li>
              <li><strong class="text-primary">100%</strong> consistenza brand tra online e showroom</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500">Dati aggiornati a dicembre 2024 – ulteriori insight saranno pubblicati a progetto completato.</p>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950/40">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Roadmap di progetto</h2>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
            {[ 
              {
                step: 'Fase 01',
                title: 'Discovery & insight',
                description: 'Interviste con team commerciale e tecnico, analisi dei touchpoint fisici e digitali, definizione KPI.'
              },
              {
                step: 'Fase 02',
                title: 'Experience design',
                description: 'Prototipi di showroom virtuali, storytelling per ogni soluzione, sviluppo sito headless e asset NFC.'
              },
              {
                step: 'Fase 03',
                title: 'Automation & AI visibility',
                description: 'Setup CRM, automazioni lead, ottimizzazioni SEO/AEO e integrazione dataset per motori AI.'
              }
            ].map(item => (
              <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/70 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">{item.step}</span>
                  <span class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 text-xs font-semibold text-primary">2 settimane</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">{item.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prossimi step</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Stiamo consolidando i materiali visuali e la documentazione finale. A breve pubblicheremo gallerie immersive e insight dettagliati del flusso lead.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
            <a href="/contattaci" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-custom-lg transition-colors hover:bg-primary-600">Prenota una consulenza</a>
            <a href="/lavori" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-primary/40 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10 dark:border-white/20 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white/10">Torna al portfolio</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
